snippet.title: Gable Steveson vs. Wyatt Hendrickson: 2025 NCAA wrestling championship (285 pounds)
snippet.description:
No. 2 Wyatt Hendrickson stunned the wrestling world with a last-second upset of No. 1 seed and two-time NCAA champion Gable Steveson. 

Subscribe to the NCAA Championship YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/NCAAChampionships?sub_confirmation=1

snippet.title: We Explored the Secret Village in the Grand Canyon
snippet.description:
Join us as we attempt this bucketlist hike through the Grand Canyon in winter vs summer! & let us know if you think Havasupai is worth the wait & expensive price tag‚Ä¶It is so easy to get started with therapy using our sponsor BetterHelp ‚ù§Ô∏è Click our link http://betterhelp.com/kandn & get 10% off your first month of therapy!

Episode 956 | Filmed March 2025 | Grand Canyon

Want to save money on flights and hotels?! Check out our all new @DailyDrop Pro! üòç‚û°Ô∏è  https://s.dailydrop.com/yt_kn-bfcm24 

‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî

‚úàÔ∏è @DailyDrop is our *FREE travel newsletter!* Get all the best travel news, tips, and tricks every weekday in your inbox by subscribing here ‚û°Ô∏è
https://faredrop.app/ytd_220827 

üì∏ Get behind the scenes content on our Instagram! @karaandnate
https://www.instagram.com/karaandnate/ 

üìß Read our Sunday Summary email to know what goes on between videos -
https://karaandnate.com/sunday-summary/ 

üé∂ Here‚Äôs where we got all of our copyright free songs used in this episode -
http://bit.ly/epidemic_sound

‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî

Who are Kara and Nate?! 

2016-2019: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FuFv4iF8wgg&t=1s 

2020-2024: https://youtu.be/ikAN9e0gBaU?si=G644UGWIqPrOzTYW

Originally from Nashville, Tennessee, we got married 2013 and were super ‚Äúnormal.‚Äù I was a teacher and Nate started a small printing business from the spare bedroom of our apartment. 

We discovered the world of ‚Äútravel hacking‚Äù while planning our honeymoon & became addicted ;)

So after 2 years of obsessively saving $35k and over 2 million miles and points, we sold our cars and apartment and left home January 10, 2016 for a ‚Äúone year‚Äù trip around the world.

Our goal was to see as many places as possible before we ran out of money and went back home to ‚Äúnormal life.‚Äù We started this channel to share our experiences with friends and family, but quickly fell in love with living on the road and found a new passion for capturing our travels through video. So we did everything we could to keep going.

4 years later, we achieved our new goal of visiting 100 countries and all 7 continents. We had no plans to slow down, until 2020 forced us to ;) Which is when we bought a converted van to start exploring our own country for the first time!

After ~2 years of van life, we are back to full time international traveling! And now we are in our 10TH YEAR of finding the best adventures the world has to offer :) 

We are incredibly grateful to be able to continue doing something we love every day. üòäüé•üåé Thank you to everyone who has been a part of our journey!

02:06 winter vs summer here
09:00 the Secret Village explained
10:40 Havasu Falls!!
12:47 our private campsite
19:27 Mooney falls
25:06 Beaver falls
27:28 MDS fail
29:38 Final thoughts

snippet.title: NASA‚Äôs SpaceX Crew-9 Re-Entry and Splashdown
snippet.description:
Watch with us as the four members of NASA's SpaceX Crew-9 mission‚ÄîNASA astronauts Nick Hague, Suni Williams, Butch Wilmore, and cosmonaut Aleksandr Gorbunov‚Äîreturn to Earth.

Suni Williams and Butch Wilmore began their mission at the International Space Station on June 6, 2024, arriving aboard Boeing's Starliner spacecraft. Nick Hague and Aleksandr Gorbunov arrived at the station on Sept. 29, 2024. Hague and Gorbunov launched to space aboard SpaceX's Dragon Freedom spacecraft, which was docked to the station since its arrival in September, and has since brought Crew-9 back home.

2:24 Return coverage begins
6:41 Meet the crew
28:14 Deorbit burn start
1:05:20 First views from WB-57 aircraft
1:09:37 Drogue chutes deploy
1:10:31 Main chutes deploy
1:12:00 Splashdown
1:33:56 Dolphins
1:38:33 Hoist
1:53:45 Hatch open
1:57:09 Crew egress

See the full schedule for Crew-9's return to Earth: https://go.nasa.gov/4iWeg8N
Learn more about Crew-9's scientific mission: https://go.nasa.gov/4bWdt5u
Follow the latest Crew-9 mission updates: https://www.nasa.gov/blogs/commercialcrew

Credit: NASA

snippet.title: Apex Legends: Beast Mode Event Trailer
snippet.description:
Become iconic across three weeks of modes! In Power Sword Royale, secure a Power Sword with its own specific abilities. Then have fun with Mozambiques for April Fools, play Solos in the final week, and conquer creator community challenges to earn rewards. Plus, check out meta updates with new Skirmisher perks and Alter ability updates.

snippet.title: Countdown To I Said I Love You First: Selena Gomez & benny blanco In Conversation | Spotify
snippet.description:
‚ÄòWe got to do what we love with who we love.‚Äù On ‚ÄúI Said I Love You First,‚Äù the collab album from fianc√©s @selenagomez and @bennyblanco, the duo explores themes of love, vulnerability, and their journey as a couple.The album was a way for them to let their guard down with each other, explore their love story, and create music in an entirely new way along with trusted collaborators including @Finneasofficial and @officialcharlixcx. By creating the project almost exclusively in benny‚Äôs home studio ‚Äì an environment neither one had ever created a full project in - Selena and benny were able to reach a newfound level of depth, comfort, and honesty in their shared music.

In this episode of Countdown To, Selena and benny discuss their lives and their love story in benny‚Äôs home in Los Angeles, CA. The couple also cruise around the city reminiscing on their favorite dates and the early days of their relationship.

localized.description:
‚ÄòWe got to do what we love with who we love.‚Äù On ‚ÄúI Said I Love You First,‚Äù the collab album from fianc√©s @selenagomez and @bennyblanco, the duo explores themes of love, vulnerability, and their journey as a couple.The album was a way for them to let their guard down with each other, explore their love story, and create music in an entirely new way along with trusted collaborators including @Finneasofficial and @officialcharlixcx. By creating the project almost exclusively in benny‚Äôs home studio ‚Äì an environment neither one had ever created a full project in - Selena and benny were able to reach a newfound level of depth, comfort, and honesty in their shared music.

In this episode of Countdown To, Selena and benny discuss their lives and their love story in benny‚Äôs home in Los Angeles, CA. The couple also cruise around the city reminiscing on their favorite dates and the early days of their relationship.

Lihat cerita ini: https://www.instagram.com/furrytail.endings/

#baikhati #hewan

KODE PREMIUMBEAT: EVU2W9PT8JPS8XOG

---------------------------
Anda Suka Video Hewan?

Berlangganan Kami di Sini: https://www.youtube.com/user/geobeats...

Tonton Video Populer Lainnya:
Gagak liar mengunjungi wanita setiap hari untuk bermain game - https://youtu.be/l_jGNTXwAAM
Pria ini memelihara opossum. Sekarang dia pikir mereka lebih pintar dari anjing - https://youtu.be/Wz7GqNCkctU
Setiap matahari terbit, burung ini mengunjungi wanita untuk berpelukan - https://youtu.be/1QuQBnv3R_Y
Kucing hitam tidak diadopsi. Kemudian wanita ini membawanya pulang - https://youtu.be/BtTygt98-1w

Ikuti Kami di Platform Lain:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/geobeats
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GeoBeatsAnimals
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/geobeatsani...

Tentang GeoBeats Animals
GeoBeats adalah perusahaan media yang berbasis di AS yang berfokus pada penceritaan kisah-kisah hewan yang menginspirasi tentang hewan-hewan dari seluruh dunia. Tujuan kami adalah membuat orang jatuh cinta pada mereka dan mempromosikan kasih sayang dan kebaikan.

Di saluran kami, kami menampilkan video-video hewan yang menarik. Anda dapat menonton video-video kucing lucu, video-video anjing lucu, video-video kucing dan anjing, kisah-kisah hewan, video-video hewan yang diselamatkan, video-video hewan yang diadopsi, dan masih banyak lagi.

snippet.title: SIDEMEN CHARITY MATCH 2025 [OFFICIAL STREAM]
snippet.description:
Sidemen Charity Match 2025

Donate here: https://www.sidemenfc.com 

On the 8th of March Sidemen FC and YouTube Allstars are coming together to play the 2025 Charity Match at Wembley Stadium.

Use the hashtag #SDMNCharityMatch to talk about the game!

OFFICIAL STREAM starts at 2:10pm GMT

Kick off time is at 3pm GMT

The Sidemen Charity Match 2025 is in aid of the following charities and funds raised will be split as follows:

Bright Side 43%
BBC Children in Need 50%
M7 Education 7%

We will also donate all of the profit we make through the match and related activities to the following charities:

Bright Side 86%
M7 Education 14%

Any donations you make are greatly appreciated and going to great causes! We hope you enjoy the match.

For full details and terms and conditions please visit https://sidemenfc.com.

Viewers of this livestream are strictly prohibited from re-streaming or rebroadcasting this content on any platform. Any unauthorised re-streaming will result in the immediate removal of the infringing livestream and a copyright strike issued to the violator.

snippet.description:

Waterman immediately ran over to celebrate with his idol Theirry Henry. snippet.title: Celebration Of Life: Donna Jordan - Drop Diamonds!
snippet.description:
Donna's last video. We are so thankful to all of you, Donna, her husband Matt, and her son James were all so happy to share our joy for quilting with everyone for so many years. Thank you to everyone for watching :)

Jordan Fabrics is a team of 18 people, including Matt, Donna, and their son James Jordan. We film, edit, cut, and sew everything you see right here in our Oregon workshop. Matt spends most of the day making very unique hand cut quilting kits, If you love sewing and quilting, but don't love the cutting, our fully pre-cut quilt and table runner kits are made for you! Visit jordanfabrics.com to view our full inventory and learn more about our kits, fabrics and pre-cuts.

id.title: Perayaan Kehidupan: Donna Jordan - Jatuhkan Berlian!
id.description:
Video terakhir Donna. Kami sangat berterima kasih kepada Anda semua, Donna, suaminya Matt, dan putranya James sangat senang berbagi kegembiraan kami dalam menjahit selimut dengan semua orang selama bertahun-tahun. Terima kasih kepada semua orang yang telah menonton :)

Jordan Fabrics adalah tim yang terdiri dari 18 orang, termasuk Matt, Donna, dan putra mereka James Jordan. Kami memfilmkan, mengedit, memotong, dan menjahit semua yang Anda lihat di bengkel Oregon kami. Matt menghabiskan sebagian besar harinya membuat perlengkapan menjahit selimut yang dipotong dengan tangan yang sangat unik. Jika Anda suka menjahit dan menjahit selimut, tetapi tidak suka memotong, perlengkapan selimut dan taplak meja kami yang sudah dipotong sebelumnya dibuat untuk Anda! Kunjungi jordanfabrics.com untuk melihat inventaris lengkap kami dan mempelajari lebih lanjut tentang perlengkapan, kain, dan potongan sebelumnya kami.

Lihat Tutorial kami yang lain di sini: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yNm8nvUq4ho&list=PLRUmC2rAbdmgmGA3GZ8_nrx5ekSIN1xzY&index=2

snippet.title: Elio | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
if any aliens are listening... the new trailer for Disney and Pixar's Elio is here!
 
See the movie, only in theaters, June 20! üåéüõ∏  
 
This summer, moviegoers will meet Elio, an 11-year-old whose biggest wish is to get abducted by aliens, as well as his Aunt Olga (voiced by recent Academy Award Winner, Zoe Salda√±a), and Glordon, Elio‚Äôs unexpected first friend who happens to be an alien. In this big-screen adventure, Elio will travel millions of miles across the universe encountering and a host of out-of-this world creatures who just might help him figure out exactly where he belongs. A new trailer and poster are now available for Disney and Pixar‚Äôs ‚ÄúElio,‚Äù which releases only in theaters June 20, 2025.
 
For centuries, people have called out to the universe looking for answers‚Äîin Disney and Pixar‚Äôs all-new feature film ‚ÄúElio,‚Äù the universe calls back! The cosmic misadventure introduces Elio, a space fanatic with an active imagination and a huge alien obsession. So, when he‚Äôs beamed up to the Communiverse, an interplanetary organization with representatives from galaxies far and wide, Elio‚Äôs all in for the epic undertaking. Mistakenly identified as Earth‚Äôs leader, Elio must form new bonds with eccentric alien lifeforms, navigate a crisis of intergalactic proportions, and somehow discover who and where he is truly meant to be. Directed by Madeline Sharafian (‚ÄúBurrow‚Äù Sparkshort), Domee Shi (‚ÄúBao‚Äù short, ‚ÄúTurning Red‚Äù) and Adrian Molina (co-screenwriter/co-director of ‚ÄúCoco‚Äù), and produced by Mary Alice Drumm (associate producer of ‚ÄúCoco‚Äù), the film features the voices of Yonas Kibreab as Elio, Zoe Salda√±a as Aunt Olga, Remy Edgerly as Glordon, Brad Garrett as Lord Grigon, Jameela Jamil as Ambassador Questa and Shirley Henderson as OOOOO.

Zach Johnson, "Millennial Farmer" adalah petani generasi ke-6 yang menghabiskan hidupnya bercocok tanam, bekerja, dan belajar di pertanian milik keluarganya. Kecerdasannya dan selera humornya yang datar menarik minat anak-anak dan orang dewasa. Sebagai produk generasi milenial, apresiasinya terhadap teknologi baru berpadu dengan etos kerjanya yang kuno, dan ia menawarkan kemampuan unik untuk menyampaikan pesannya dengan cara yang sesuai dengan petani seumur hidup maupun mereka yang tidak memiliki pengetahuan tentang pertanian. Dengan meningkatnya kesadaran konsumen tentang asal makanan mereka, Zach telah mengidentifikasi perlunya suara independen dari garis depan pertanian. Zach aktif mempromosikan pertanian dengan berbagi pengalaman sehari-harinya di dunia pertanian sambil memberikan edukasi dari petani ke petani untuk membantu memfasilitasi percakapan kolaboratif antara petani dan masyarakat.

it.title: Come i dazi di Trump stanno influenzando la nostra agricoltura

snippet.title: How Space X Crew 10 Transfer & Return to Earth Works?
snippet.description:
Take your personal data back with Incogni! Use code AITELLY at the link below and get 60% off an annual plan: http://incogni.com/AITELLY

This is SpaceX‚Äôs pride and joy‚Äîthe Falcon 9, designed under the visionary leadership of  Elon Musk.
Sitting atop the rocket is Crew Dragon, carrying four astronauts on a critical mission to rescue and replace two crew members aboard the International Space Station.
The reason these two NASA astronauts are stranded traces back to Boeing‚Äôs Star liner.
On its first-ever astronaut mission, launched on June 5, 2024, the vehicle encountered unexpected issues, leaving the crew awaiting a safe return. 

During the docking procedure, the Star liner encountered issues with its Reaction Control System thrusters.

The spacecraft‚Äôs software initially flagged five s as non-operational, affecting its ability to maneuver in all six degrees of freedom.

Although four of the thrusters were eventually restored, the underlying cause of the malfunction remains unclear.

We're here to take a closer look at how SpaceX's Crew Dragon rescue process works.

In the event of a rescue, a replacement crew would travel , where the Falcon 9 rocket stands ready for liftoff.

Falcon 9 is a two-stage rocket designed for reliability and efficiency.
Unlike rockets that rely on a single engine, its first stage is powered by nine Merlin engines.

This design provides an added layer of safety‚Äîif one engine fails, the remaining engines can compensate, ensuring a smooth and controlled ascent.

The second stage, responsible for propelling Crew Dragon into orbit, is power++ed by a single Merlin engine.

At the very top of the rocket sits the capsule named Crew Dragon‚Äîdesigned to safely transport astronauts to and from space.

snippet.title: NASA‚Äôs SpaceX Crew-9 Undocking
snippet.description:
Watch as the four members of NASA's SpaceX Crew-9 mission‚ÄîNASA astronauts Nick Hague, Suni Williams, Butch Wilmore, and cosmonaut Aleksandr Gorbunov‚Äîundock from the International Space Station and begin their journey home to Earth.

Crew-9's SpaceX Dragon spacecraft is scheduled to undock from the International Space Station at 1:05 a.m. EST (0505 UTC). After undocking from the station, Crew-9 is scheduled to splash down off the coast of Florida at 5:57 p.m. EDT (2157 UTC), ending their multi-month mission in low Earth orbit.

See the full schedule for Crew-9's return to Earth: https://go.nasa.gov/4iWeg8N
Learn more about Crew-9's scientific mission: https://go.nasa.gov/4bWdt5u
Follow the latest Crew-9 mission updates: https://www.nasa.gov/blogs/commercialcrew/

Credit: NASA

snippet.title: Every shot from THREE-HOLE PLAYOFF | THE PLAYERS | 2025
snippet.description:
Check out every shot from the three-hole playoff at THE PLAYERS Championship 2025, where Rory McIlroy outlasted J.J. Spaun to claim his second PLAYERS victory and his 28th win of his PGA TOUR career.

SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh

The PGA TOUR heads to Ponte Vedra Beach, Florida this week for the THE PLAYERS Championship at TPC Sawgrass. Defending champion and World No. 1 Scottie Scheffler returns to THE PLAYERS Stadium Course at TPC Sawgrass looking to extend his legacy and become the first golfer to three-peat at THE PLAYERS. World No. 2 Rory McIlroy is hoping to recreate some magic at in Ponte Vedra Beach, FL. McIlroy, winner of this year‚Äôs AT&T Pebble Beach Pro-Am, captured the THE PLAYERS in 2019, but has had a bit of a mixed bag at TPC Sawgrass since then. With over 75 yards added, THE PLAYERS will be decided over the 7,352 yards that THE PLAYERS Stadium Course at TPC Sawgrass has to offer. Alongside last week's Arnold Palmer Invitational winner Russell Henley, other notable players in the field include Xander Schauffele, Ludvig √Öberg, Hideki Matsuyama, Justin Thomas and Rickie Fowler with a total of 48 of the world‚Äôs top 50 playing in this year's event.

02:58 The team that's got it badly wrong

snippet.title: NASA's SpaceX Crew-9 Hatch Close
snippet.description:
Watch as the four members of NASA's SpaceX Crew-9 mission‚ÄîNASA astronauts Nick Hague, Suni Williams, Butch Wilmore, and cosmonaut Aleksandr Gorbunov‚Äîbegin the final preparations for their return to Earth, currently targeted for Tuesday, March 18.

After entering their SpaceX Dragon spacecraft, the spacecraft's hatch will be closed on the Crew-9 explorers. After hatch closure, Crew-9 is scheduled to undock from the International Space Station at 1:05 a.m. EDT (0505 UTC) on Tuesday, March 18.

See the full schedule for Crew-9's return to Earth: https://go.nasa.gov/4iWeg8N
Learn more about Crew-9's scientific mission: https://go.nasa.gov/4bWdt5u
Follow the latest Crew-9 mission updates: https://www.nasa.gov/blogs/commercialcrew/

Credit: NASA

snippet.title: Surviving the Tornado ‚Äì March 14 2025 Disaster in the Missouri Ozarks
snippet.description:
Description:
On the night of March 14 2025 at approximately 9:51 PM, a powerful tornado tore through our region in the southern Missouri Ozarks (Oregon County). As we took shelter, weather alerts flooded our phones, warning of the devastation to come. This video documents the raw reality of experiencing such a violent storm firsthand.

We are incredibly fortunate‚Äîno lives were lost among our family or animals‚Äîbut the damage to our land and forest is severe. Sadly, many of our neighbors lost everything. This storm serves as a sobering reminder of nature‚Äôs power and the resilience required to rebuild.

If you‚Äôre in a position to help those affected by these storms, please consider supporting local relief efforts. We will provide updates as we assess the damage and begin the recovery process.

Thank you for watching, and stay safe out there.

Pada malam tanggal 14 Maret 2025 sekitar pukul 9:51 malam, tornado dahsyat menerjang wilayah kami di Missouri bagian selatan Ozarks (Kabupaten Oregon). Saat kami berlindung, peringatan cuaca membanjiri ponsel kami, memperingatkan tentang kehancuran yang akan datang. Video ini mendokumentasikan kenyataan pahit tentang mengalami badai yang begitu dahsyat secara langsung.

Kami sangat beruntung‚Äîtidak ada nyawa yang hilang di antara keluarga atau hewan kami‚Äîtetapi kerusakan pada tanah dan hutan kami parah. Sayangnya, banyak tetangga kami kehilangan segalanya. Badai ini menjadi pengingat yang serius tentang kekuatan alam dan ketahanan yang dibutuhkan untuk membangun kembali.

Jika Anda berada dalam posisi untuk membantu mereka yang terkena dampak badai ini, mohon pertimbangkan untuk mendukung upaya bantuan lokal. Kami akan memberikan informasi terbaru saat kami menilai kerusakan dan memulai proses pemulihan.

Terima kasih telah menonton, dan tetaplah aman di luar sana.

#TornadoSurvival #MissouriOzarks #StormDamage #TornadoOutbreak #storm #stormshelter #damage

snippet.title: NASA's SpaceX Crew-10 Docks With the ISS: All the Highlights in 13 Minutes
snippet.description:
After a 28-hour flight aboard the Crew Dragon Endurance, NASA's SpaceX Crew-10 mission successfully docked with the International Space Station. Watch all the highlights from the mission that will return NASA astronauts Sunita Williams and Barry Wilmore to Earth.

Read more on CNET.com
NASA Crew-10 Docks With ISS To Trade Places With 'Stranded' Astronauts https://cnet.us/5zl

0:00 Intro
0:47 View from ISS and Crew Dragon
1:35 330 Meters from ISS docking
2:20 View from ISS external cameras
2:40 View from inside Dragon Endurance
3:23 View of docking and navigation lights
4:03 Approaching way point two
5:10 Mission Control Teams clear for docking
5:57 Ready for final approach
7:02 Dragon Docks with ISS
9:19 ISS Crew prepares to welcome astronauts aboard
10:25 Crew-10 thanks ground crews
